flowchart TD
    I[GitHub Issue] --> S[Spec / Plan / Tasks when needed]
    S --> B[Branch]
    B --> T[Local Tests / Gates]
    T --> E[Evidence Handoff]
    E --> P[Pull Request]
    P --> R[Reviewer-Agent]
    R --> H[Human Approval]
    H --> M[Squash Merge]
    M --> C[Issue Comment / Close]
    C --> L[Living Evidence Portfolio]
    L --> D[Status / Architecture Docs]
